### Update Appointment Status
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED",
  "notes": "Appointment confirmed",
  "changedByStaffId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174003",
  "invoiceAmount": 50.00,
  "invoiceDetails": "Oil change service"
}

### Get Appointment Status Log
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/status-log

### Get Tracking Appointments by Status
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/appointments/tracking?status=PENDING